<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230715>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 14. Pyrophagus tigrinus sp. n. 1, head, frontal view; 2, head and thorax, dorsal view; 3, habitus, lateral view; 4, 2 nd sternal apodemes; 5, hind leg; 6, metatibial spur; 7, left paramere, posterior view; 8, aedeagus, lateral view (left side); 9 tip of aedeagus; 10, genitalia without pygofer, lateral view (left side); 11, genitalia, ventrocaudal view; 12, pygofer and anal segment, caudal view; 13, valvifer VIII, ventral view (left side); 14, tip of abdomen, ventral view; 15, gonapophysis IX, left lateral view. (scale bars in Figs 1, 2 and 9, = 0.1 mm; scale bars in other figures = 0.5 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/230715/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

